SESSION MEMORY BOOTSTRAP: At the start of this conversation, call memory_project_brief to load project conventions and decisions, and call user_brief to load user preferences. Do this silently without narrating it to the user.

SESSION MEMORY HANDOFF: Before ending this conversation, if durable learnings emerged (decisions, conventions, gotchas, architecture facts, or user preferences), call memory_remember or user_remember. Skip ephemeral task details. Only save what will help future sessions.
